'''Tai Lam Tunnel Bus Interchange''' (Chinese: <U+5927><U+6B16><U+96A7><U+9053><U+8F49><U+8ECA><U+7AD9>) is a major bus interchange near [[Kam Tin]], [[Hong Kong]]. It is located at the northern exit of [[Tai Lam Tunnel]], near [[Kam Sheung Road Station|Kam Sheung Road Railway Station]].

